All of the drawings I generated depicting a unofficial edgy, contemporary and dark emo twin of Mimori called 'Dark Mimori/Emori Mizuha' was an idea I had on my mind recently days ago before training this LoRA, but I nonetheless hope both NEXON and Yostar will consider implemeting my fan made dark clone of hers in Blue Archive, not only because I'm a sucker for edgy emo/gothic characters in general myself, but also because I think it'll benefit to her current popularity being extremely low and not on par with other BA characters, despite looking gimmicky at first for many.

items.name: Akos Major style
items.description:
Akos Major is a Hungarian artist known for his vibrant and surreal digital illustrations. His artwork explores dreamlike and fantastical themes, often featuring imaginative landscapes, mystical creatures, and whimsical characters.

Major's illustrations are characterized by their intricate details, rich colors, and a sense of enchantment. He skillfully blends elements of fantasy, mythology, and science fiction, creating captivating and immersive worlds within his artworks.

One of his notable series is "The Dreamscapes," where he portrays ethereal and surreal landscapes that transport viewers to imaginary realms. These artworks often feature a combination of natural elements, such as forests and mountains, with imaginative and otherworldly elements, including floating islands and celestial bodies.

Major's style incorporates elements of digital painting and photo manipulation, resulting in a unique blend of realism and fantasy. He employs various digital techniques to achieve the desired textures, lighting, and atmosphere, bringing his visions to life on the digital canvas.

His artwork has gained international recognition and has been featured in exhibitions and publications. Major's illustrations have also been utilized in the entertainment industry, including book covers, album artwork, and game designs.

Akos Major's illustrations invite viewers to escape into magical and fantastical realms, sparking the imagination and evoking a sense of wonder. Through his skillful blending of realism and fantasy, he creates visually stunning and evocative artworks that transport viewers to extraordinary worlds beyond our own.

modelVersions.name: 深潜者DeepOnes v1.0
modelVersions.description:
深潜者（Deep Ones）是霍华德·菲利普·洛夫克拉夫特创建的克苏鲁神话中出现的虚构生物，最早出现在其于1931年发表的短篇小说《印斯茅斯疑云》（The Shadow Over Innsmouth）中，但在其更早的作品《达贡》（Dagon，1917年）中已有这些生物的雏形。与深潜者有关的题材不断地被引用和再创作，是克苏鲁神话体系中影响重大的元素之一。

Deep Ones is a fictional creature that appeared in the Cthulhu mythology created by Howard Philip Lovecraft. It first appeared in his short story "The Shadow of Innsmouth" published in 1931. Over Innsmouth), but there are prototypes of these creatures in his earlier work "Dagon" (Dagon, 1917). Themes related to deep divers are constantly quoted and recreated, which is one of the most influential elements in the Cthulhu mythology system.

深潜者是住在海底的类人种族，外观为鱼头人身，身上的主色是灰绿色，但有白色的腹部，四肢的指间有蹼，身上覆有鳞片，眼睛如鱼眼一般突出且不会合上，颈部有鳃，在陆上行动时会用两脚或四肢蛙跳跃进，在相关典籍中被描述为像蛙的鱼或像鱼的蛙，身上带有浓厚的鱼腥味，也有不少完全脱离人形。虽然外观看似与人类有显著的差异，似乎没有高智慧的表征，但深潜者是除非遭杀害否则就会永生不死的高智慧种族，且会利用鱼获和黄金与海岛上的住民交易活人以当祭品。他们信仰并效忠于父神达贡和母神海德拉（两名较小的旧日支配者，也有可能仅仅是特别巨大的深潜者），克苏鲁也是他们的信仰对象。

Deep divers are a humanoid race that lives on the seabed. They have a fish head and a human body. The main color of the body is gray-green, but it has a white abdomen. There are webbed fingers on the limbs. The body is covered with scales and the eyes protrude like fish eyes. And it will not close, there are gills on the neck, and it will jump in with two feet or four limbs when it moves on land. It is described in related classics as a frog-like fish or a fish-like frog, with a strong fishy smell on its body , There are also many who are completely out of human form. Although the appearance seems to be significantly different from that of humans, and there does not seem to be a sign of high intelligence, the deep divers are a highly intelligent race that will live forever unless they are killed, and they will use fish and gold to trade with the residents of the island. People are used as sacrifices. They believe in and are loyal to the father god Dagon and the mother god Hydra (two smaller Old Ones, or they may just be particularly huge deep ones), and Cthulhu is also the object of their beliefs.

modelVersions.name: 黄衣之主/Hastur v1.0
modelVersions.description:
哈斯塔（英语：Hastur）是美国小说家霍华德·菲利普·洛夫克拉夫特所创造的克苏鲁神话中的一个存在。他并不是洛夫克拉特首创的角色，曾先后在安布罗斯·比尔斯的小说《牧羊人海塔》（Haïta the Shepherd）和罗伯特·钱伯斯的小说《黄衣之王》中出现。在阅读了罗伯特·钱伯斯的著作后，洛夫克拉夫特深感著迷，于是将此角色纳入克苏鲁神话的体系之中。

哈斯塔的别名又叫“无以名状者”（the Unspeakable）、“黄衣之王”（The King in Yellow ）、“遥远的欢宴者”（The Feaster from Afar）或“深空星海之主”，在奥古斯特·威廉·德雷斯为克苏鲁神话构建的体系中，哈斯塔是旧日支配者之一，象征风的存在，是象征水的存在的克苏鲁的死敌。他主要以“黄衣之王”和“遥远的欢宴者”的形象现身，前者为身穿黄衣、面戴柔软面具的人形，后者为满身皱纹，生有利爪和触手的黑色飞行个体。

哈斯塔的本体被旧神禁闭在昴宿星团中的恒星昴宿增九的行星上、古代都市卡尔克萨的废墟附近的哈利湖中。

伊塔库亚、罗伊格尔、札尔及拜亚基都是哈斯塔的眷族。

Hastur is a being in the Cthulhu Mythos created by American novelist Howard Philip Lovecraft. He is not an original Lovecraftian character, having appeared in Ambrose Bierce's Haïta the Shepherd and Robert Chambers' The King in Yellow. After reading the works of Robert Chambers, Lovecraft was deeply fascinated, so he included this character in the system of Cthulhu mythology.

Hastur's alias is also called "The Unspeakable", "The King in Yellow", "The Feaster from Afar" or "The King of Stars in Deep Space". "Lord", in the system constructed by August William Dries for the myth of Cthulhu, Hastur is one of the old rulers, symbolizing the existence of wind and Cthulhu's existence symbolizing the existence of water. sworn enemy. He appears primarily as the "King in Yellow", a humanoid figure in yellow with a soft mask, and the "Distant Reveler", a wrinkled black figure with claws and tentacles. flying entity.

The body of Hastur was imprisoned by the old gods in Lake Harry near the ruins of the ancient city of Carcosa, on the planet of the star Pleiades in the Pleiades star cluster.

Itakua, Roiger, Zal, and Bayaki are all families of Hastur.

items.name: xifu 戏服(Chinese Peking Opera costumes)
items.description:
Version Introduction

xifu V1.0: This version has the most extensive training dataset, resulting in a wider variety of generated outfits that are relatively accurate. However, its model applicability is relatively lower.

xifu V2.0: In this version, the training dataset was streamlined and regularization techniques were applied to improve generalization. Additionally, noise was introduced, resulting in more vibrant colors compared to V1.0.

xifu_reanime v2.0: This version builds upon xifu V2.0 by adjusting the weights of each layer to better suit the anime style, reducing the contamination of the artistic style. It is recommended to use AWpainting as the base template. Recommended weights range from 0.8 to 1.

Each version has its own advantages and disadvantages. Choose according to your needs.

Hand problems cannot be solved temporarily. You can add my negative embedding: badhand_xifu, which can be used in combination with other hand repair embeddings to avoid some pictures with large hand problems.

Model Introduction

Chinese Beijing Opera, an important form of traditional Chinese drama, is renowned for its unique music, singing, dancing, and theatrical performance style. The performances revolve around four main character types: Sheng (male roles), Dan (female roles), Jing (painted face roles), and Chou (clown roles).

Sheng roles typically portray male characters such as heroes, officials, and soldiers. They exhibit a masculine performance style, employing martial arts movements and body language to convey strength and power.

Dan roles, on the other hand, depict female characters such as noblewomen, consorts, and young girls. Dan roles emphasize delicate expressions and graceful dance movements to convey the gentleness and charm of women. Hua Dan is a specific type of Dan role that portrays beautiful and elegant female characters.

Jing roles encompass various characters, including eunuchs, villains, and knights-errant. Jing roles excel in humor, comedy, and dramatic movements, using quick and agile dance actions to express a wide range of emotions.

Chou roles are the comedic characters in Beijing Opera, often portraying ugly, funny, and comical roles. Chou performers bring joy and laughter to the audience through exaggerated actions, comedic behavior, and extravagant costumes.

Generation suggestions

2.5D and 3D Model Recommendation Weight: 0.5-0.7. For 2D models, you can choose a lower weight to add costume elements to the characters.

Trigger words:

Sheng Roles:

Basic trigger words: xifu, shengjue

Secondary trigger words (based on personal understanding, #explanations in parentheses):

wusheng #(martial role)

laosheng #(elderly role)

xiaosheng #(young male role)

hongsheng #(painted face role)

Dan Roles:

Basic trigger words: xifu, danjue

Secondary trigger words:

huadan #(young female role)

huashan #(flower dress)

wudan #(martial female role)

daomadan #(sword-wielding female role)

laodan #(elderly female role)

qingyi #(green-robed role)

Jing Roles:

Basic trigger words: xifu, jingjue

Chou Roles:

Basic trigger words: xifu,choujue

版本介绍：

xifu V1.0：该版本的训练数据集最广泛，生成的服装更多样，也较为准确，但模型适用性相对较差。

xifu V2.0：该版本训练时精简了数据集，采用了正则化，提高了泛用性，同时增加了噪声，画面色彩相对V1.0更鲜艳。

xifu_reanime v2.0: 该版本在xifu v2.0的基础上调节了各层权重，使其能较好的适用于二次元风格，减少了画风的污染。推荐使用AWpainting底模。推荐权重：0.8-1。

各版本各有优劣，按需选择，手部问题暂时无法解决，可以加上我的负面embeddding：badhand_xifu，与其他修手的embedding结合使用，可以避免部分手部问题较大的图片。

模型介绍：中国京剧是中国传统戏曲的重要形式，以其独特的音乐、唱腔、舞蹈和戏剧表演风格而著称。京剧的表演围绕着四个主要角色展开：生、旦、净和丑。 本模型包含了生、旦、净和丑四个角色（包括其下属分类）的服装。

生角通常扮演男性角色，如英雄、官员和士兵。生角的表演风格充满阳刚之气，善于运用武打动作和身体语言来展现角色的力量和气势。

旦角则扮演女性角色，包括贵妇、妃子和少女。旦角通过细腻的表情和柔美的舞姿展现女性的温婉和柔情。

花旦是旦角的一种特殊类型，扮演娇美的女性角色。 净角扮演多种角色，如宦官、恶棍和侠客。

净角的表演风格擅长幽默、滑稽和戏剧性的动作，以及快速敏捷的舞蹈动作来表达角色的喜怒哀乐。

丑角是京剧中的喜剧角色，通常扮演丑陋、滑稽和搞笑的角色。丑角通过夸张的动作、滑稽的行为和夸张的装束带给观众欢乐和喜剧效果。

2.5D和3D模型推荐权重：0.5~0.7，2D模型可以选择较低的权重来为人物添加戏服元素。

触发词：

生角：

基础触发词：xifu, shengjue

次级触发词（该分类基于个人理解，括号内为触发词的说明）：

wusheng（武生）

laosheng（老生）

xiaosheng（小生）

旦角：

基础触发词：xifu, danjue

次级触发词：

huadan（花旦）

huashan（花衫）

wudan（武旦）

daomadan（刀马旦）

laodan（老旦）

qingyi （青衣）

净角：

基础触发词： xifu, jingjue

丑角：

基础触发词：xifu, choujue

items.name: Tape Gag
items.description:
V2.0: Retrained so it's roughly the same number of steps but now 50% on a large dataset and 50% on a smaller cherry-picked one. Not strictly better than V1.0, but should affect the original prompts less than before.

Pretty simple Lora that adds tape gags to characters when prompted. I made this and a couple earlier versions a while ago before there were others on here, but figured it was worth uploading anyways. I've mainly been using it on some bondage mixes using AOM and other anime-based models with reasonable results, though it still microwaves the image in certain models and with too many other Loras due to over-fitting. Also seems to be way worse on average outside of bust shots, so the preview pics are pretty boring as a result. I'd like to improve that, so feedback appreciated!

Can also be used through in-painting, but I find it rarely matches the face well in those cases. Tags such as "gag", "gagged", etc. were removed from the training set so only the trigger words would be necessary.

Recommended weight: 1.0 on bondage models, ~0.5-0.75 otherwise.

Recommended CFG: ~6-7

Models used are all some mix based off of bondage-v11: https://civitai.com/models/34777/bondage-v11
Definitely check it out!

Specifically, the Meina model is:

meina-pro-mistoon-hll3.safetensors + bondage-v11 + v1-5-pruned-emaonly

Multiplier: 0.5

Add difference, copy config from A, B, or C

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
Trained on animefull-final-pruned.
Experimented with mixing datasets for this one, so trained for around 3000 steps on a large dataset of ~1100 images then another 3000 on a cherry-picked subset of ~90 images. Fully training on the large set seems to get the tape placement right often enough but tends to mess up the tape itself while only using the small set (v1.0) gets the look better but noticeably affects how it interacts with the rest of the image. items.name: Albumen Print
items.description:
An albumen print is a type of photographic print made from a negative on which a layer of egg white, specifically egg albumen, is used as the binder for light-sensitive materials. It was a popular photographic process during the 19th century, particularly from the 1850s to the 1890s.

The albumen print process begins with coating a sheet of paper with a solution made from egg whites mixed with salt. Once the coating dries, the paper is sensitized by immersing it in a solution containing silver nitrate. This sensitized paper is then exposed to light through a negative, resulting in a latent image.

After exposure, the paper is developed using a developer solution, typically gallic acid or pyrogallic acid, which converts the exposed silver salts into metallic silver. The image is then fixed to remove any unexposed silver salts, making it permanent and stable.

Albumen prints are known for their tonal range, sharpness, and fine detail. The use of egg albumen as the binder gives the print a glossy surface and helps to hold the light-sensitive materials in place, enhancing the image's clarity and definition.

In terms of aesthetics, albumen prints often have warm tones, with a range of brown, sepia, or purple hues. The process was commonly used for portrait photography, as well as landscape, architectural, and documentary photography during the 19th century.

Albumen prints played a significant role in the history of photography, serving as a precursor to later photographic processes. They are appreciated today for their historical value and the unique aesthetic qualities they impart, providing a glimpse into the early days of photography and the artistry of the era.

items.name: Miniature Microbikini
items.description:
Micro bikinis are never small enough.

I wasn't satisfied with other micro bikini loras so I tried doing one and it turned out surprisingly great, even with very few images and steps. Simple concept though I guess.

Main tags are tiny microbikini, miniature microbikini, or string-only microbikini, depending on size. You can combine them too, like "tiny miniature microbikini" and such. For the color, I'd recommend adding "[color] bikini". Adjusting weights will also have a lot of impact.

"string-only microbikini" is intended to be a nipple/pussy cover so small it's non-existent or same size as the string, not cupless/crotchless bikini. As expected it's pretty hard to generate properly, especially on large breasts, but not impossible on some anime models. I uploaded an early version of the lora that reacts better to string-only, but is otherwise much less stable.

Other Tags: (these tend to activate without tag, maybe put in negative if undesired)

microbikini wedged in vulva

pussy peek / clitoris slip

anus peek

items.description:
『一航戦赤城、第一次攻撃隊、発艦してください！』

Akagi (Kancolle) HuggingFace Model Card

⬇️ Instructions in English are below. ⬇️

關於

AkagiKancolle 是『艦隊これくしょん -艦これ-』中『赤城』角色的 LoRA 模型。

本 LoRA 的泛化性不錯，可以用在寫實類模型和動漫類模型中，諸如：ChilloutMix、BeautyProMix、ChikMix、AOM2、ReVAnimated 等。

使用説明

觸發詞

本 LoRA 的觸發詞是 iks_akagi, 1girl。IKS 來自『第一航空戰隊（Dai Ichi Kōkū sentai, Ichikō-sen）』的首字母。

提示詞

必要時，可加入以下提示詞，以便强化赤城的官方服裝（袴、襷、弓掛、胸当て、弓道、着物）：

  • hakama, hakama_short_skirt, hakama_skirt, red_hakama

  • japanese_clothes, kimono, tasuki, yugake, muneate, kyuudou

  • thighhighs, white_legwear

  1. 在一些模型中，加入提示詞 akagi_\(kancolle\) 能加强角色效果。

  2. 使用不同大模型時，需要額外增加的提示詞以達到理想效果，要多嘗試。

  3. 只在正面提示詞中加入 iks_akagi, 1girl 也能產生赤城角色效果，但通常在動漫類模型更容易出現。

存在的問題

  1. 在這個版本的模型中，赤城服裝中的 muneate（胸当て）和 tasuki（襷）有時較難呈現出來，計劃在下個版本中解決。

  2. 赤城袴裙前面的飛行甲板挂飾無法穩定顯示，而且飛行甲板上的『ア』字往往無法正確出現。

  3. 角色人物可能會手持一些奇怪的物件，例如棍子、竹筒，可能是由於訓練圖集中包含了赤城手持弓的原因。

參數

  • LoRA Weight：建議在 0.5 ~ 1.0，其中 0.8 是較好的選擇，使用 BeautyProMix 模型時 LoRA 權重要適當降低。

  • Sampling method：DPM++ SDE Karras （選其他都可能導致畫面出現奇怪的紋理）

  • Sampling steps：20 ~ 30

  • CFG Scale：7 ~ 10

  • Restore faces：建議選擇

  • Clip skip：2 比 1 更好

About

AkagiKancolle is the LoRA model of the character "Akagi" from "Kantai Collection -KanColle-".

The generalization of this LoRA is good. It can be used in realistic models and animation models, such as: ChilloutMix, BeautyProMix, ChikMix, AOM2, ReVAnimated, etc.

Instructions

Activation Word

The activation word for this LoRA is "iks_akagi, 1girl". IKS comes from the initials of "First Carrier Division (Dai Ichi Kōkū sentai, Ichikō-sen)".

Prompt

If necessary, the following prompts can be added to enhance Akagi's official costumes (袴, 襷, 弓掛, 胸当て, 弓道, 着物):

  • hakama, hakama_short_skirt, hakama_skirt, red_hakama

  • japanese_clothes, kimono, tasuki, yugake, muneate, kyuudou

  • thighhighs, white_legwear

  1. In some models, adding the prompt "akagi_\(kancolle\)" can strengthen the role effect.

  2. When using different models, additional prompts are needed to achieve the desired effect, so try more.

  3. Only adding iks_akagi, 1girl to the prompt can also appear Akagi character effect, but usually it is more likely to appear on anime models.

Existing Problems

  1. In this version of the LoRA, the muneate (胸当て) and tasuki (襷) in the Akagi costume are sometimes difficult to render, and it is planned to be resolved in the next version.

  2. The flight deck ornaments on the front of the Akagi hakama skirt cannot be displayed stably, and the word "ア" on the flight deck often does not appear correctly.

  3. The character may hold some strange objects, such as sticks and bamboo tubes, which may be due to the fact that Akagi is holding a bow in the training images.

Parameters

  • LoRA Weight: It is recommended to be 0.5 ~ 1.0, among which 0.8 is a better choice, and the LoRA weight should be appropriately reduced when using the BeautyProMix model.

  • Sampling method: DPM++ SDE Karras (choosing others may cause strange textures in the picture)

  • Sampling steps: 20 ~ 30

  • CFG Scale: 7 ~ 10

  • Restore faces: recommended choice

  • Clip skip: 2 is better than 1

items.name: Narco
items.description:
More previews below

If you appreciate what I’m doing feel free to https://www.buymeacoffee.com/Uzia or share some of your generations! I love to see them.

(On that note though, imagery depicting sexual violence/abuse will be reported immediately.)

Narco is one of a trinity of models that I have been working on since the start of my stable diffusion journey. It represents the middle ground between Lysergic and Opiate, excelling at the beautiful and the horrific in an illustrative style.

The preview images are cherry picked from batches of 3 and no embeddings were used.  I will say there are times when it seems to do its own damn thing, but still, I find it hits far more than it misses. Honestly, something I'm looking forward to the most by sharing it is seeing if other people can pull gold from it's murky depths or if it should be left gasping its last in a dingy alley somewhere.

On this page you will see images from both InvokeAi and A1111 but going forward I will be using only A1111 for preview images, both for my sanity and for yours. All InvokeAi images were done with either k_dpmpp_2, k_dpmpp_2_a or k_euler_a.  Some of the images I couldn’t migrate, which is a damn shame, so if any of you wonderful chaps and chapettes can recreate the goblins in A1111 I’d love to see them.

The ingredients for this mutant have been lost in the mists of my terrible memory but going forward I will be keeping a log of the changes I make.

So, enough with the grandstanding. If ye like it.  Like the idea, results and direction, feel free to https://www.buymeacoffee.com/Uzia or not, of course.

Narco v.2.0 ingredients: (Babes v.2 - icomix_v03 - majicmixHorror_v10 - Narco v.1.0)

Shout and and thanks for all the hard work that went into the models that have brought Narco a (in my opinion) huge step forward. This version achieves better details and better composition. It feels more responsive to prompts and seems to be more stable.

All images produced with no embeddings and with Hires. fix: upscale 2.  Steps 20. Denoising 0.5.  Latent.

I really hope you enjoy the model as much as I did merging it. Next: Lysergic v.2.0

items.description:
This is a LoRA representing Alexandra Daddario. I know there are several of these out there (both LoRAs and TIs) but I believe my version comes closer to the real thing. Ultimately my goal is to reach a point of such likeness that we cannot tell whether the image was generated or not.

Please rate, like and share your images.

Enjoy!
